 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n花枝的確=墨魚無錯，但係烏賊並不=魷魚<br />\n<br />\n花枝/墨魚 英文都叫cuttlefish  係呢個樣:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Sepia_officinalis_%28aquarium%29.jpg/270px-Sepia_officinalis_%28aquarium%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F4%2F4b%2FSepia_officinalis_%2528aquarium%2529.jpg%2F270px-Sepia_officinalis_%2528aquarium%2529.jpg&h=58e62018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n魷魚(squid)係呢個樣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/e9KLSzm1RAE/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fe9KLSzm1RAE%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=4273f1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而無論係魷魚(squid)定係花枝/墨魚(cuttlefish)，都可以叫做烏賊(Decapodiformes（十腕總目）)<br />\n<br />\n即係阿媽(魷魚/花枝/墨魚)一定係女人(烏賊)，但係女人(烏賊)唔一定係阿媽(魷魚/花枝/墨魚)<br />\n<br />\n所以[烏賊]依個字你解做cuttlefish或者squid其實都無問題(個人見到大部份解成cuttlefish多D)<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n題外話:<br />\n<br />\n以烏賊娘既身體構造其實似魷魚(squid)多D<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RpggAY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpggAY8.jpg&h=f5ab122b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過台灣翻譯成花枝(cuttlefish)娘 可能因為個名女性化會靚D"},{"pid":"46d337fd977e6709ad0261eee348ea98f8da4f1c","tid":1122363,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a833a70a2122595f20465f5b827fe0adfc9f374","tid":1122363,"uid":246648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"22b159620225b1e343fa521e9e99095c8ce6a948","tid":1122363,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2369792745ebfc16ee2b8974d9ee2a6f3c1219f2","tid":1122363,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T05:54:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"等陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" clas